Paul H. Pickle 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Operating Officer at MICROSEMI CORP, Paul H. Pickle  made $3,389,004 in total compensation.  Of this total $440,000 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $2,894,010 was awarded as stock and $54,994 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


