Executive Profile
Paul H. Pickle  President and Chief Operating Officer, Microsemi CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships47$3,389,004As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Paul H. Pickle has been President of Microsemi Storage Solutions, Inc. since January 15, 2016. Mr. Pickle has been the President and Chief Operating Officer at Microsemi Corporation since November 2013. He served as an Executive Vice President of Integrated Circuits Group at Microsemi Corporation from 2012 to 2013 and served as its Senior Vice President of Integrated Circuit Group from 2011 to 2012. He served as General Manager of Analog and SoC Products at Microsemi ... Corporation from 2009 to 2012. Mr. Pickle served as Corporate Vice President of Microsemi Corporation from 2009 to 2011. He also served Vice President of Worldwide Applications Engineering from 2004 to 2009 and Product Marketing Manager of Integrated Products Group from 2000 to 2004. He has been a Director of Microsemi Storage Solutions, Inc. since January 15, 2016.Read Full Background




